{
  "texts": [
    "Teaching reflective writing had no statistically significant impact on the response to question Q6, \"During interactions with patients, I consider how their personal thoughts and feelings are influencing the interaction\" (n = 24, 82.76%, p = 0.096).",
    "However, the post-session survey results for questions Q1-Q5 were (n = 25, 86.2%, p < 0.001; n = 26, 89.6%, p < 0.001; n = 24, 82.7%, p = 0.002; n = 23, 79.3%, p = 0.014; n = 25, 86.2%, p = 0.008), respectively; and the results for questions Q7-Q10 were (n = 22, 75.8%, p = 0.009; n = 23, 79.3%, p = 0.010; n = 21, 72.4%, p = 0.012; n = 24, 82.7%, p = 0.004), respectively.",
    "This showed the impact of teaching as a significantly greater percentage of students chose \"definitely agree\" after the session.",
    "Moreover, a significantly higher percentage of students chose \"extremely important\" in response to question Q11, \"How important do you believe reflective practice is in dental education?\"",
    "(n = 22, 75.8%, p = 0.009)."
  ]
}